<section class="comment-content comment">
<p>Nah. You can still get rich completely through accident, happenstance, luck, and chance. I believe this is how pretty much every honest, decent person got rich.</p>
<p>The power of chance in the world is huge and people systematically underestimate it (psychological studies bear this out: people routinely find and believe rationales for things which are truly, simply random).</p>
</section>
