<cite><b class="fn">Philip Pilkington</b> </cite><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20230122074248/https://www.nakedcapitalism.com/2011/08/what-is-debt-%e2%80%93-an-interview-with-economic-anthropologist-david-graeber.html#comment-452380"><time datetime="2011-08-26T09:07:11-04:00">August 26, 2011 at 9:07 am</time></a> </header>
