<p>Even within the same tribal unit, I do not believe credit came first.</p>
<p>I believe sharing came first.</p>
<p>Somehow sharing was corrupted into borrowing.</p>
<p>Borrowing is sharing with a need-to-be-paid-back requirement.</p>
<p>So, again, credit did not come first.</p>
<p>Any primatologists around?</p>
