<section class="comment-content comment">
<p>The Austrian Economists have a vested interest in the barter theory of money since gold, one of their chief fetishes (usury being another), is considered the ultimate barter item. See Mises&#8217; &#8220;Regression Theory of Money.&#8221;</p>
<p>But hypocritically, the smarter gold bugs desire government acceptance of gold as money thus validating the Chartalists.</p>
</section>
